    "While urban areas have benefited from the IJS, rural courts still rely on manual processes.",
    "Additionally, the system has faced criticism over data security concerns.Outcomes.",
    "The IJS has led to more efficient case management and greater coordination between justice sector agencies.",
    "However, addressing regional disparities and enhancing data security will be critical for the system's long-term success.",
